About Us

   Hi, Everyone! It is nice to meet you. Welcome to Chili Pepper Madness,
   the food blog run by Mike and Patty Hultquist, a couple of spicy food
   lovers. Chili Pepper Madness is a special tribute to all things chili
   peppers, including chili pepper recipes... [109]LEARN MORE ABOUT US

